  <brief_title>Evaluation of Hysterectomy After Chemoradiation Therapy for Stage IB2/II Cervical Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Phase III Trial Evaluating the Impact of Hysterectomy After Chemoradiation Therapy for Stage IB2/II Cervical Cancer</official_title>
